{
  "name": "junoglow",
  "description": "Soft analog synth pads breathing dreamy and warm, a Juno chorus shimmering in the sun. Warm Juno-style additive pads with gentle chorus shimmer and soft bleeps: a round sub-pad ground floor, a soft-attack pad lead singing the melody, a playful pluck-synth bleep answering, a plush chorused tone in the middle, soft synth-bell pings and tiny arpeggiating droplets up top, a big chorused bloom swell, a shimmering detuned-saw cloud, and the faint warm hiss of the machine. A major pentatonic at A=432, additive and clean, hall reverb, plush and bright, retro-warm and optimistic, never cold or dark.",
